ComicInfo.Title: Part Six
ComicInfo.Series: Nancy Drew: The Death of Nancy Drew
ComicInfo.Summary:
WHO TRIED TO KILL NANCY DREW? WHO STILL WANTS HER DEAD? This final issue of the much-talked-about series will finally unveil the mastermind behind Nancy’s attempted murder… but will it lead to one of the Hardy brothers deaths?
